Yeah, but he also taught George Stosey.

42:45.001 --> 42:48.065
And he did not have a high opinion on that.

42:48.105 --> 42:49.866
No, I know he taught W. Amazing.

42:49.906 --> 42:57.494
I don't know how to get into that, but that's a pretty good question.

42:57.634 --> 42:59.776
That was the old Yale.

