Say again, I'm sorry?

43:00.657 --> 43:01.678
That was the old Yale.

43:01.858 --> 43:02.479
Yeah, the old Yale.

43:02.499 --> 43:05.061
That was the first product.

43:05.081 --> 43:08.625
And had it not changed to the new Yale, I would not come back.

