He's their best-selling author, Samuel Elliot Morrison.

49:01.647 --> 49:08.074
And there was a very, very good text, college text division.

49:08.114 --> 49:13.860
But they published some semi-trade books.

49:13.880 --> 49:16.703
Oh, I think more than semi-trade books.

49:16.723 --> 49:18.786
